sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant API as API handler
    participant Coord as Coordinator
    participant Node as Node
    participant Store as BadgerDB
    participant IBLT as IBLTState
    participant Peers as Other HRW replicas

    Client->>API: PUT key, JSON value
    API->>Coord: Put(req)
    Coord->>Coord: HRW.Replicas(key, members, RF)

    alt if node not replica
        Coord->>Peers: Forward Put to Replica
    else 
        Coord->>Node: Put(key, value)
        Node->>Store: persist new field entries (atomic batch)
        Node->>IBLT: update with old/new entries
        Node-->>Coord: ts, written entries
        Coord-->>Client: PutResponse{ts}
        Coord->>Peers: async PushEntries (fire-and-forget)
        Note over Coord,Peers: Failures are reconciled by anti-entropy (see sync diagram)
    end
